## Get Purchase Details by Purchase ID [/api/v1.0/purchases/{purchaseId}]

### Get Purchase Details by Purchase ID [GET]

+ Parameters 
    + purchaseId: `5664cjyceae` (string, required) - Unique ID assigned to identify a purchase record. You can use this ID to retrieve the purchase details from the Purchase database.<br><br> The purchase details includes:   
     + Information about the customer.
     + Information about the <@ creator_popup @>. Applicable in case of offline booking made by an agent.
     + Payment status of the purchase.
     + Summary of charges.
     + Invoice summary. 
     + List of items, including the information about the item price, selected payment options, item-level payment status, earnings, confirmation details, and <@ consumer_popup @> details. 
     + Additional information about the purchase, if any. 

